                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>On December 13, 1954, the United States and Guatemala signed at Washington an
                    agreement providing for development assistance to Guatemala, which entered into
                    force on the same date. For text of the agreement, see 5 UST (pt. 3) 2972, or
                    TIAS No. 3155. For additional information, see Department of State press release
                    715, dated December 13, 1954, in the Department of State <hi rend="italic"
                        >Bulletin</hi>, December 27, 1954, page 985.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
